v><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,2,1,2)">Three projects covering regression classification and clustering using scikit-learn</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,2,2,2)">Only complete Kaggle competitions</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,2,3,2)">Memorise all algorithms</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-2"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-3"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q4</span>What is a Data Scientist?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,3,0,1)">A computer scientist who studies data</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,3,1,1)">A professional who analyses data and builds models to extract business insights and support decisions</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,3,2,1)">Only a statistician</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,3,3,1)">An ML engineer</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-3"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-4"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q5</span>What is the first Python library to learn for data manipulation?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,4,0,2)">TensorFlow</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,4,1,2)">Scikit-learn</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,4,2,2)">NumPy and Pandas</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,4,3,2)">PyTorch</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-4"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-5"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q6</span>What is fast.ai known for?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,5,0,1)">A fast training framework only</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,5,1,1)">A top-down practical deep learning course that teaches cutting-edge techniques to practitioners quickly</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,5,2,1)">A type of neural network</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,5,3,1)">A cloud ML service</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-5"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-6"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q7</span>What makes Kaggle competitions valuable for learning?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,6,0,1)">Prize money</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,6,1,1)">Real datasets with leaderboards that show how your solution compares and community notebooks to learn from</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,6,2,1)">They are easy</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,6,3,1)">Kaggle provides solutions</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-6"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-7"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q8</span>What does an MLOps Engineer specialise in?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,7,0,2)">Research into new algorithms</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,7,1,2)">Data analysis</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,7,2,2)">Infrastructure pipelines and operations for deploying and maintaining ML systems in production</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,7,3,2)">User interface design</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-7"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-8"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q9</span>What is Papers with Code?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,8,0,1)">A journal of programming papers</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,8,1,1)">A resource connecting ML research papers with open-source implementations for easy reproduction</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,8,2,1)">A code review platform</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,8,3,1)">An ML competition</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-8"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-10-9"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q10</span>What statistics knowledge is foundational for ML?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,9,0,1)">Advanced calculus only</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,9,1,1)">Mean median variance correlation probability and hypothesis testing — these underlie how every ML algorithm works</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,9,2,1)">Linear algebra only</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,10,9,3,1)">None — ML is purely practical</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-10-9"></div></div></div><div class="quiz-actions"><span class="quiz-answered-count" id="qcount-10"><span>0</span>/10 answered</span><button class="quiz-submit-btn" id="qsub-10" onclick="submitQuiz(10)" disabled>Submit &#8594;</button></div><div class="quiz-result" id="qres-10" style="display:none"></div></div></div></div>
